  "response": "I can't know what's going on inside your head. Whether you \"think too much\" depends on your personal experience. Some signs might include:\n\n1. Overthinking can look like:\n- Constant worrying\n- Difficulty making decisions\n- Analyzing past events repeatedly\n- Stress and anxiety\n- Trouble sleeping due to racing thoughts\n\n2. Potential benefits of thinking deeply:\n- Problem-solving skills\n- Self-awareness\n- Detailed planning\n- Creativity\n\n3. If overthinking is causing you distress, you might consider:\n- Mindfulness techniques\n- Talking to a therapist\n- Practicing meditation\n- Journaling\n- Setting limits on rumination\n\nOnly you can truly assess if your thinking patterns are helpful or harmful. Would you like to discuss this more specifically?",
